  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200&deg;C/ 180&deg;C (fan)/ 400&deg;F/ Gas 6</p>\r\n<p>Boil a kettle</p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>tricoloured pasta twists</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a large pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p>\r\n<p>Cook the pasta for 8-10 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "image": "/images/instructions/breaded-smoked-fish-and-creamy-courgette-pasta/step-1.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, top, tail and grate the<strong> courgette<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "image": "/images/instructions/breaded-smoked-fish-and-creamy-courgette-pasta/step-2.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine&nbsp;the <strong>panko&nbsp;breadcrumbs</strong>&nbsp;with 2 tbsp&nbsp;<span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span>&nbsp;<strong>olive oil</strong>&nbsp;and a pinch of&nbsp;<strong>pepper</strong>&nbsp;in a small bowl</p>\r\n<p>Cut the <strong>smoked basa fillets</strong> in half&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>smoked basa</strong> to a baking tray and top with the<strong>&nbsp;panko breadcrumbs </strong></p>\r\n<p>Put the tray in the oven for <span class=\"text-highlight\">6-8 min</span>, or until cooked through</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "image": "/images/instructions/breaded-smoked-fish-and-creamy-courgette-pasta/step-3.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop the<strong> dill </strong>finely, including the stalks</p>\r\n<p>Chop the <strong>chives</strong> finely</p>\r\n<p>Zest half the<span class=\"text-danger\"> [whole]</span> <strong>lemon</strong><span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> (try to grate lightly with a micro-plane or sharp box grater and avoid grating the white pith, as this is very bitter!)</p>\r\n<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "image": "/images/instructions/breaded-smoked-fish-and-creamy-courgette-pasta/step-4.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the <strong>pasta</strong> is cooked, drain it and set aside</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "image": "/images/instructions/breaded-smoked-fish-and-creamy-courgette-pasta/step-5.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of&nbsp;<strong>olive oil </strong>over a medium heat</p>\r\n<p>Once hot, add the grated <strong>courgette</strong>, <strong>chopped</strong>&nbsp;<strong>chives</strong> and <strong>garlic </strong>with a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and cook for 2 min</p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>cr&egrave;me fra&icirc;che</strong>, <strong>lemon zest</strong> and the juice of 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span>&nbsp;<strong>lemon</strong></p>\r\n<p>Season with and pinch of&nbsp;<strong>pepper </strong>and cook for 2 min or until thickened slightly</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "image": "/images/instructions/breaded-smoked-fish-and-creamy-courgette-pasta/step-6.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add&nbsp;the <strong>drained</strong>&nbsp;<strong>pasta</strong>&nbsp;to the sauce and give everything a good mix up &ndash; this is your <strong>creamy courgette pasta</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "image": "/images/instructions/breaded-smoked-fish-and-creamy-courgette-pasta/step-7.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>crispy baked fish</strong>&nbsp;over the<strong> creamy courgette pasta</strong></p>\r\n<p>Garnish with the <strong>chopped dill&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8
    }
  ],
